item.title: Remix: How Artist Scherezade Garcia Came to Work and Exist on Her Own Terms
item.description: Listening to Scherezade Garcia talk about her art and her creative process is watching someone relive the many ways she has made herself free— from other’s scrutiny, from expectations, from the need to justify her very existence. Alicia visited Scherezade’s studio and spoke with her about the notion of selling the Caribbean as “paradise”, the business of being a working artist, and what it means to be home. Follow Scherezade on Twitter @scherezade_art and IG @scherezadegarcia... Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/uUMa3TSo
